Enhanced Statistical Analysis Workbook
======================================

Worksheets:
1. Executive Summary - Key findings and metrics
2. Correlation Analysis - All correlation matrices and significance tests
3. Economic Impact Analysis - Property values, retail sales, employment impacts
4. Geographic Analysis - TOD vs Non-TOD comparisons, spatial statistics
5. Priority Gaps Analysis - Ranked list with all scoring factors
6. Monte Carlo Simulation - Risk analysis and confidence intervals
7. Cost-Benefit Analysis - Detailed financial modeling
8. Sensitivity Analysis - Scenario testing and impact assessment
9. Statistical Appendix - Raw data and detailed calculations

Key Features:
- Interactive dashboards with slicers and filters
- Pivot tables for data exploration
- Charts and graphs for visualization
- Statistical calculation worksheets
- Scenario analysis tools
- Data validation and error checking

This file would contain all the statistical analysis results from Sections 10.2, 10.3, and 10.4 in an interactive Excel format for easy exploration and further analysis.